# This file is intentionally free of active environment variable assignments.
# Do NOT commit real secrets (API keys, tokens, passwords) to version control.
#
# Instead:
#   - Create a local .env file that is ignored by git (via .gitignore), or
#   - Configure environment variables in your deployment environment.
#
# Example variables (uncomment and set locally, do not commit real values):
# DEVCYCLE_API_KEY=your_real_api_key_here
# DEVCYCLE_ENVIRONMENT=production